articles.title: Hello.
articles.contents:
Hi!
My name is Johannes and I am a PhD candidate in the department of Clinical Psychology and Epidemiology, and an IT admin, both at the Faculty of Psychology at the University of Basel. In my research i combine the two by leveraging technology (machine learning, natural language processing, virtual reality, psychophysiology) to understand and improve mental health.
